            <p style="font-size:9px;">Omni-Loans MAKES NO REPRESENTATIONS OR WARRANTIES OR CLAIMS WITH REGARDS TO ANY REPRESENTATIONS, WARRANTIES AND CLAIMS MADE BY THE VENDOR.  OMNI LOANS ACTING SOLELY AS A THIRD PARTY LENDER TO FACILITATE THE BORROWERS PURCHASE OF PRODUCTS OR SERVICES OFFERED BY THE VENDOR.</p>


            <p style="font-size:9px;">OMNI-LOANS MAKES NO REPRESENTATIONS OR WARRANTIES THAT THE LOAN WILL FIX, REPAIR OR IMPROVE YOUR CREDIT OR THAT THE LOAN INFORMATION WILL BE POSTED TO YOUR CREDIT PROFILE.  THE CREDIT REPORTING AGENCIES ALONE MAKE THE DECISIONS AS TO WHAT INFORMATION IS POSTED TO YOUR CREDIT PROFILE.</p>

            <p style="font-size:9px;">THIS EXCLUSION OF LIABILITY SHALL APPLY TO THE FULLEST EXTENT PERMITTED BY LAW. THIS PROVISION SHALL SURVIVE THE TERMINATION OF THIS AGREEMENT.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
            <p class="dc-statement">13. CONTINUING EFFECTIVENESS OF THIS AGREEMENT</p>
            <p style="font-size:9px;">We may assign the Loan, with or without the benefit of this Agreement, to any other financial institution or other entity or person without your consent, but you may not assign this Agreement without our consent. This Agreement is also binding upon and beneﬁts our successors and your permitted assigns, heirs, and personal representatives.</p>
